query:
SELECT DISTINCT m.id, m.title, COUNT(t.id) as trade_count 
FROM markets m 
INNER JOIN trades t ON m.id = t.marketId 
GROUP BY m.id, m.title 
ORDER BY trade_count DESC 
LIMIT 1;
